BuildUp.Loading.long.description: The BuildUp or the Work Instruction are in the loading state. Once loaded it will allow you to activate the buildup.
PositionMatrix.Title: Position Matrix
BuildUp.Deactivate.short.description: Display the BuildUp or Workinstruction Views of the selected object in the viewer.
BuildUp.Deactivate.long.description: You can use the widget preference default mode to choose the default display
BuildUp.Activate.short.description: Remove the BuildUp or Workinstruction Views of the selected object in the viewer.
BuildUp.Activate.long.description: You can use the widget preference default mode to choose the default display
Graph.Deactivate.short.description: Display Graph View of the selected object in the viewer
Graph.Deactivate.long.description: Graph View is a graphical representation of product flow links and time constraints links between different operations using the Project Evolution Review Technique (PERT).
Graph.Activate.short.description: Remove Graph view of the selected object in the viewer
Graph.Activate.long.description: Graph View is a graphical representation of product flow links and time constraints links between different operations using the Project Evolution Review Technique (PERT).
PartFabrication.Show.short.description: Displays graphics of material part to be fabricated in viewer
PartFabrication.Show.long.description: Exclusively displays raw material graphics from which the part is to be fabricated, and hides main 3D graphics. To view the main 3D graphics, toggle this command again.
PartFabrication.Hide.short.description: Removes the display of the material part to be fabricated.
PartFabrication.Hide.long.description: Removes the display of material graphics and shows the main 3D graphics in the viewer.
